Source.Contents:
/#
   The type that indicates the length of the resource.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.ResourceLength {
  # The length unit of the resource. For example, pages (pdf, text documents) or time (audio, video files).
  lengthUnit : string

  # The length value of the resource.
  lengthValue : decimal

}

lengthUnit.Doc: The length unit of the resource. For example, pages (pdf, text documents) or time (audio, video files).
lengthUnit.Name: lengthUnit

lengthValue.Doc: The length value of the resource.
lengthValue.Name: lengthValue
